column16: Kurt Suzuki grounds into a double play, pitcher Louis Coleman to shortstop Alcides Escobar to first baseman Eric Hosmer.   Aaron Hicks out at 2nd.
Gerardo Parra lines out to shortstop Alcides Escobar.
Adam Jones doubles (24) on a line drive to left fielder Alex Gordon.   Nolan Reimold scores.    Manny Machado to 3rd.
J.   Hardy pops out to first baseman Eric Hosmer.
Jimmy Paredes pops out to catcher Drew Butera in foul territory.
Kurt Suzuki grounds out, third baseman Mike Moustakas to first baseman Eric Hosmer.
Torii Hunter flies out to left fielder Paulo Orlando.
Eddie Rosario grounds out to first baseman Eric Hosmer.
